x_Preview" style=3D"color: inherit;"><span class=3D"MJXp-math" id=3D"MJXp-S=
pan-51"><span class=3D"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic" id=3D"MJXp-Span-52">p</span></s=
pan></span>. This purple slider
